; $VER: CopyToRAM&Run 47.1 (26.01.2021)
; Copies HDToolBox to RAM and runs it from there. 
  
; If < 1 MB RAM free then show not enough RAM message and quit.

avail >env:MemTotB total
If not val $MemTotB GE 1000000
  RequestChoice "                  HDToolBox copying process suspended" "At least 1 MB of available RAM is required to install AmigaOS 3.2!*n*n                       Aborting procedure..." "Okay" >NIL:
  Quit
EndIf

copy >NIL: AmigaOS3.2CD:Tools/HDToolBox(|.info) RAM:
Protect >NIL: RAM:HDToolBox.info +rw
WBLoad RAM:HDToolBox

quit